<a href="/questions/404108-i-found-this-book-cover-glowing-in-the">I found this book cover glowing in the dark last night. 
Anyone else notice that the yellow books on the cover glow??
creepy as all get out. I thought I was hallucinating. But it really does glow. I could see my hand prints.</a>
