<span id="freeTextContainer3679161300752609886">Highly original page turner with a wonderful mix of dusty bookstores and old bibliophiles, alongside the digital age of Googling masters and venture capitalists, and how both worlds have their ideas and uses in the mystery that emanates from Mr Penumbra&apos;s book shop :-) 8 out of 12.<br/><img src='https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1591984735ra/29636539.gif' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1608017223i/30530442._SX540_.jpg' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/></span>
  <span id="freeText3679161300752609886" style="display:none">Highly original page turner with a wonderful mix of dusty bookstores and old bibliophiles, alongside the digital age of Googling masters and venture capitalists, and how both worlds have their ideas and uses in the mystery that emanates from Mr Penumbra's book shop :-) 8 out of 12.<br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1591984735ra/29636539.gif" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1608017223i/30530442._SX540_.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"></span>
