<span id="freeTextContainer1393022223066358338">Robin Sloan is the author of the novels Mr. Penumbra&apos;s 24-Hour Bookstore and Sourdough. He grew up near Detroit and now splits his time between the Bay Area and the internet.</span>
  <span id="freeText1393022223066358338" style="display:none">Robin Sloan is the author of the novels Mr. Penumbra's 24-Hour Bookstore and Sourdough. He grew up near Detroit and now splits his time between the Bay Area and the internet.</span>
